  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    British High Commission Cyprus webinar series: technology and women
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">A talk with Amanda Pinto QC, Chair of the Bar Council for 2020 on 'technology and women: how important are they to justice and the Bar?'</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
